# Language detection overrides for GitHub Linguist

# Mark Roff/documentation files as documentation (won't count toward language stats)
*.1 linguist-documentation
*.man linguist-documentation
*.roff linguist-documentation

# Common documentation patterns
docs/** linguist-documentation
ProofofConcept/** linguist-documentation

# Vendor dependencies (if any)
venv/** linguist-vendored
env/** linguist-vendored
*.egg-info/** linguist-vendored

# Mark Jupyter notebooks as documentation (optional - remove if you want them counted)
# *.ipynb linguist-documentation

# Ensure Python is properly detected
*.py linguist-detectable